data.description:
Sunset Park legal 2 family brownstone house for sale. This three story house offers a unique
combination of comfort and design. The first floor features a 3 bed and 1 bath duplex with the
walk in level. Second floor features 3 beds and 1 bath. There is also a full finished basement.
This home is located near N and R train stations. It is convenient to all that 5th Ave has to offer,
shopping, restaurants schools and supermarkets. Building size is 20x45 sq ft sitting on a
20x100 sqft lot. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own this house.
